This paper deals with learning on social networks, which falls under the category of social and information networks (cs.SI). The paper also discusses different models of agent behavior, which involves machine learning (cs.LG) and data science (cs.DS). The paper also analyzes the efficiency of learning, which can be categorized under multi-agent systems (cs.MA). Finally, the paper discusses the convergence of dynamics, which is related to game theory and social choice (cs.SOC).
